articles.title: Malaysian women shock defending champions Japan - New Straits Times
articles.description: KUALA LUMPUR: The youthful Malaysian women’s team showed incredible fighting spirit in coming from behind to stun defending champions Japan 3-2 in their opening Group Y match of the Badminton Asia Team Championships today.
